# Home page
msgid "Interactive Learning Platform"
msgstr "Interaktiv ta'lim platforma"

msgid "Master Skills Through"
msgstr "Ko'nikmalarni o'yin orqali"

msgid "Play"
msgstr "o'rganing"

msgid "Deepland is a gamified, interactive learning platform where education meets adventure. Earn XP, collect badges, and learn with friends."
msgstr "Deepland — bu o'yin va sarguzashtlar bilan to'la interaktiv ta'lim platformasi. XP to'plang, nishonlar yig'ing va do'stlaringiz bilan birga o'rganing."

msgid "Start Learning"
msgstr "O'rganishni boshlash"

msgid "Join Community"
msgstr "Jamiyatga qo'shilish"

msgid "Why Deepland?"
msgstr "Nima uchun Deepland?"

msgid "Gamified Progress"
msgstr "O'yin orqali rivojlanish"

msgid "Learn through interactive tasks and get instant feedback. Watch your XP grow and level up like in a game."
msgstr "Interaktiv topshiriqlar orqali o'rganing va tezkor natijalar oling. XP darajangiz o'sishini kuzating."

msgid "Smart Challenges"
msgstr "Aqlli masalalar"

msgid "From coding to logic, our challenges are designed to keep you sharp and curious about the world."
msgstr "Dasturlashdan mantiqiy masalalargacha — bizning topshiriqlarimiz sizni doimiy ravishda rivojlantirishga mo'ljallangan."

msgid "Meet the Guides"
msgstr "Yo'lboshchilar bilan tanishing"

msgid "Four unique characters—Nova, Pixel, Lyra, and Byte—will accompany you on your learning journey."
msgstr "To'rtta noyob qahramon — Nova, Pixel, Lyra va Byte — o'rganish sayohatingizda sizga hamrohlik qiladi."

msgid "Meet Your Companions"
msgstr "Hamrohlaringiz bilan tanishing"

msgid "The Balanced Mentor"
msgstr "Muvozanatli murabbiy"

msgid "Guides with wisdom and patience, ensuring steady progress and stability."
msgstr "Donolik va sabr-toqat bilan yo'l ko'rsatadi, barqaror rivojlanishni ta'minlaydi."

msgid "The Analytical Creator"
msgstr "Tahliliy ijodkor"

msgid "Blends logic with emotion to help you make well-rounded decisions."
msgstr "Mantiq va his-tuyg'ularni uyg'unlashtiradi, to'g'ri qarorlar qabul qilishga yordam beradi."

msgid "The Master of Logic"
msgstr "Mantiq ustasi"

msgid "Brings order and structure to every task, making learning efficient."
msgstr "Har bir topshiriqqa tartib va tuzilma olib keladi, o'rganishni samarali qiladi."

msgid "The Creative Spark"
msgstr "Ijodiy uchqun"

msgid "Injects fun and creativity into the process, keeping motivation high."
msgstr "Jarayonga quvonch va ijodkorlik qo'shadi, motivatsiyani yuqori tutadi."

msgid "Ready to start your adventure?"
msgstr "Sarguzashtni boshlashga tayyormisiz?"

msgid "Join thousands of learners and start mastering new skills today."
msgstr "Minglab o'quvchilarga qo'shiling va bugundan yangi ko'nikmalarni egallashni boshlang."

msgid "Launch Deepland"
msgstr "Deeplandni ishga tushirish"

